*[[바다표범]] (''bada-pyobeom'') [[hair]] [[seal]] (earless), literally, "[[sea]] [[leopard]]"
*[[해표]] ([[海豹]], ''haepyo'') [[hair]] [[seal]] (earless), literally, "[[sea]] [[leopard]]" 

